    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Each Vampire heritage has a specific revulsion listed in their heritage entry.</p><p>A creature must Interact to brandish the revulsion for 1 round (similar to Raising a Shield).</p><p>If you involuntarily come within 10 feet of your revulsion, you can attempt a @Check[will|dc:25] save as a free action, which has the concentrate trait.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> you overcome your revulsions for 1 hour</p><p><strong>Success</strong> as critical success, but the time is [[/r 1d6 #rounds]]{1d6 rounds}</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> you become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1}</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> you are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.sDPxOjQ9kx2RZE8D] for 1 round.</p>",
